{"id":"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale","title":"Set the runtime locale manually","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"set-the-runtime-locale-manually\" translation-result=\"on\">手動設定執行時語言環境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#set-the-runtime-locale-manually\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Set the runtime locale manually<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#set-the-runtime-locale-manually\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<!--todo: The Angular CLI sets the locale ID token as part of the translation. -->\n<!--todo: To override the provider for the locale ID token. -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 的初始安裝中已經包含了美國英語（<code>en-US</code>）的語言環境資料。當你將 <code>--localize</code> 選項與 <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> 命令一起使用時，<a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 會自動包含語言環境資料並設定 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The initial installation of Angular already contains locale data for English in the United States (<code>en-US</code>).\nThe <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> automatically includes the locale data and sets the <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> value when you use the <code>--localize</code> option with <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> command.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要將應用程式的執行時語言環境手動設定為自動值以外的一種，請完成以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To manually set the runtime locale of an application to one other than the automatic value, complete the following actions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/ | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/</code></a> 目錄的 language-locale 環境組合中搜索 Unicode 語言環境 ID。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Search for the Unicode locale ID in the language-locale combination in the <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/ | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/</code></a> directory.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">設定 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 令牌。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下範例將 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 的值設定為法語的 <code>fr</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example sets the value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> to <code>fr</code> for French.</p>\n\n<code-example header=\"src/app/app.module.ts\" path=\"i18n/doc-files/app.module.ts\" region=\"locale-id\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a>, <a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a> } from '@angular/core';\nimport { <a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a> } from '@angular/platform-browser';\n\nimport { AppComponent } from '../src/app/app.component';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  imports: [ <a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a> ],\n  declarations: [ AppComponent ],\n  providers: [ { provide: <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a>, useValue: 'fr' } ],\n  bootstrap: [ AppComponent ]\n})\nexport class AppModule { }\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n - cli\n - cli/build\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#set-the-runtime-locale-manually\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale#手動設定執行時語言環境\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/\n-->"}